description: Welcome home to Penthouse 6G at The Ceinture! This custom-designed 2 bedroom + den, 2-bathroom residence offers a private balcony, garage parking space & additional storage. Luxury finishes include custom kitchen cabinetry, Bosch SS appliances, quartz countertops with waterfall edges, built-in speakers, oak engineered HW flooring throughout, and an in-unit w/d. The current owner has tastefully upgraded the home with custom lighting, sophisticated wallpaper, upgraded mirrors, electronic blinds and fully built-out closets as well as a media console. The Ceinture is a 54-unit professionally managed luxury condominium building newly constructed in 2021. The building offers a concierge, full fitness center, a club room with a catering kitchen and a 2,000+ sq ft roof deck with several outdoor seating areas and gas grilling stations. Ideally located steps to The Broadway Red Line T-stop, the best restaurants/shops in South Boston and on the border of both the South End and Seaport District.
